file.name: descriptions.yml
file.content:
---
openapi: "3.0.1"
paths:
  /simple.SimpleService/DoSomething:
    post:
      summary: "Do Something"
      description: "Let's do something"
      operationId: "simple.SimpleService.DoSomething"
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/simple.SomeInput"
          application/protobuf:
            schema:
              type: "object"
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/simple.SomeOutput"
            application/protobuf:
              schema:
                type: "object"
components:
  schemas:
    simple.SomeInput:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        anotherField:
          type: "string"
          format: "string"
        someField:
          type: "string"
          description: "Some field top\nSome field side"
          format: "string"
      description: "This is some input"
    simple.SomeOutput:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        yetAnotherField:
          type: "string"
          description: "Yet another field top\nYet another field side"
          format: "string"
      description: "This is some output"
